                Phone: +1 (555) 123-4567
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <h2>9. Changes to This Policy</h2>
            <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on our website with an updated effective date.</p>
        </div>

